msgid ""
"A format is a standardized way that information is encoded for for "
"storage on a digital storage medium. Archivematica recognizes hundreds of"
" file formats by extracting format information from `PRONOM`_, a "
"technical registry of file formats maintained by the National Archives of"
" the UK."
