#: ../../user-manual/preservation/preservation-planning.rst:632
msgid ""
"Normalization is the process of taking a file of a given format and "
"transforming it into another format for a stated purpose, such as access "
"or preservation - for example, Archivematica could contain rules to "
"convert a PNG file to a JPG for  access and a TIFF for preservation."
